  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    net.sf.jsqlparser.expression.ExpressionVisitor, net.sf.jsqlparser.statement.select.SelectItemVisitor

    public class ColumnNameFinder
extends com.uwi.visitors.abst.AbstractColumnNameFinder
    The ColumnNameFinder class retrieves a list of columns from SelectItem. Logic for handling SelectItem item function is added here. Currently only the count function has been implemented.
